    desc: 'Reads diagrams, charts, tables nested in PDFs, scanned documents, and screenshots. Opens up research and document-heavy work in finance, legal, analytics, and architecture.',
    icon: 'M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z',
    color: '#60A5FA',
