    bench: 'Core Analytics',
    desc: 'First model to break 90% on complex, long-running analytical tasks — a 10-point jump over Opus. The strongest finance-first model ever tested on general finance and reasoning.',
    icon: 'M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z',
    color: '#CC9560',
  },
  {
    title: 'Scientific Research',
    score: '89.4%',
    bench: 'SciQA',
    desc: 'Deep understanding of scientific papers, experimental design, and cross-domain synthesis. Handles literature review, hypothesis generation, and methodology critique at expert level.',
    icon: 'M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z',
    color: '#F472B6',
  },
  {
    title: 'Knowledge Work',
    score: '94.6%',
    bench: 'KnowledgeBench',
    desc: 'The longer and more complex the task, the larger Fable 5\'s lead. Strategic memos, policy drafts, competitive analysis, and comprehensive reporting — all at a level exceeding Opus.',
    icon: 'M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253',
    color: '#E8B4B0',
  },
  {
    title: 'Tool Use & Agents',
    score: '96.1%',
    bench: 'ToolBench',
    desc: 'Near-perfect tool orchestration with multi-step planning, parallel execution, and adaptive error recovery. Powers the most sophisticated AI agent workflows on any platform.',
    icon: 'M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z',
    color: '#A78BFA',
  },
